    "description": "I've gone far too long without a new reel (seeing as my last personal reel was made 14 years ago), and I had so many works begging for some place to be shown that the process of curation was extremely grueling. \n\nI'd enjoy to edit another reel for the more corporate, design-led, and brand-focused work, but I wanted to celebrate my love for characters and the handcrafted, textured, and illustrated styles of the really talented artists I collaborated with for all these years.\n\nIf you want me to animate for you, just visit my website zenzuke.com and get in contact.\n\nI hope you like it, and we'll see if this one lasts another 14 years!",
